    "description": "《蜀末》是一款包含肉鸽和卡组构筑元素的回合制战斗游戏，你可以免费体验序章内容。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >序章和正式版的区别</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>角色：序章包含1个角色，正式版包含3个。<br></li><li>卡牌：序章包含60张卡牌，正式版包含163张卡牌。<br></li><li>宝物：序章包含21个宝物，正版版包含61个宝物。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>复刻经典三国：从最简单的杀、闪、桃、酒开始，收集宝物，构筑多种多样的流派挑战强敌！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023440/extras/b1b39c2ed5b217fb98840ba65bd15c0f.poster.avif?t=1738938934\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023440/extras/b1b39c2ed5b217fb98840ba65bd15c0f.webm?t=1738938934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023440/extras/b1b39c2ed5b217fb98840ba65bd15c0f.mp4?t=1738938934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>搭配肉鸽关卡：从多种线路、变化事件中选择你的前进方向。每个不同选择，都会引发不同结局。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023440/extras/48d06390399d0a5c5a0b249620a69146.poster.avif?t=1738938934\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023440/extras/48d06390399d0a5c5a0b249620a69146.webm?t=1738938934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023440/extras/48d06390399d0a5c5a0b249620a69146.mp4?t=1738938934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>不重样的宝物：每个宝物都是独一无二，自由组合，产生神奇的化学反应。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023440/extras/5e917d772c7e8b72eafd35095ec529ef.poster.avif?t=1738938934\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023440/extras/5e917d772c